了一根临时铝管。</p><p>据报道，布宜诺斯艾利斯警察局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078">已突击搜查CasaSur酒店，以寻找进一步的证据</a>。</p><p>佩恩的去世引发了关于为年轻艺术家提供更多保护的讨论，歌曲作家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯在他去世后呼吁音乐产业停止让未成年人加入男孩乐队</a>。佩恩第一次参加<em>《X Factor》</em>试镜时年仅 14 岁，在节目第 10 季期间成为 One Direction 成员时年仅 16 岁。</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Sharon-Osbourne">莎朗·奥斯本</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">指责音乐产业“让佩恩失望”</a> ，她在 Instagram 上发帖写道：“利亚姆，我的心很痛。我们都让你失望了。当你需要他们的时候这个行业在哪里？当你进入世界上最艰难的行业之一时，你还只是个孩子。谁在你的角落里？安息吧我的朋友。” </p><figure id="attachment_3805683" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805683" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805683" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805683" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Andrew Chin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>与 One Direction 一起参加选秀节目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·维塞尔 (Katie Waissel</a> ) 此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“对年轻艺术家的关心和支持</a>”。同样，在同一季节目中获得第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">在向佩恩致敬的同时，也公开反对“对年轻明星的剥削和牟取暴利”。</a></p><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀还表示，佩恩去世后，音乐产业“给年轻人带来了巨大的压力”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>也表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">作为一名“绝望”想要实现佩恩曾经取得的成功的艺术家，感觉被欺骗了“这个行业‘成功’的承诺是什么。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">此后发起了一份新的请愿书，呼吁制定新的法律来保障音乐行业艺术家的心理健康</a>。请愿书已获得超过10万签名。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-cassidy-leaving-liam-payne-alone-in-argentina-before-his-death-will-haunt-her-for-the-rest-of-her-life-3806450">凯特·卡西迪 (Kate Cassidy) 在利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世前将他独自留在阿根廷，这将“在她的余生中困扰着她”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
