06457" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806457" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806457" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1.jpg" alt="查普尔·罗恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-erika-goldring-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806457" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：Erika Goldring/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>在采访的其他地方，尼克斯讨论了她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lindsey-buckingham">林赛·白金汉的</a>混乱关系，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-nicks-says-she-gave-lindsey-buckingham-300-million-chances-in-fleetwood-mac-3806018">在弗利特伍德麦克给了林赛·白金汉“3亿个机会”</a> 。</p><p>尼克斯最后一次与他联系是在 2023 年他们已故乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christine-mcvie">克里斯汀·麦克维 (Christine McVie</a> ) 的葬礼上。</p><p>尼克斯谈到庆祝活动时说：“克里斯汀在诺布上降下了一场飓风，这就是我们发生的地方。” “老实说，几乎把整个地方都炸毁了。拆除了整个甲板，所有的装饰和一切。所以这有点疯狂。我们都感觉她就在那里，因为那真的很激烈。</p><p> “我唯一一次和林赛说话就是在那里，大约三分钟。我尽可能长时间地与林赛打交道。你不能说我没有给过他三亿多的机会。”</p><p>尼克斯还表示，她希望<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/daisy-jones-the-six"><em>《黛西·琼斯与六人组》</em></a>第二季<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/stevie-nicks-wants-daisy-jones-the-six-to-rewrite-fleetwood-mac-history-3806435">能够改写弗利特伍德麦克的历史。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-nicks-defends-chappell-roan-says-its-good-shes-not-going-to-drop-dead-for-all-you-people-3806447">史蒂